title: Eastarjet Adds New Okinawa Service to Seoul From Late October 2015
text:
Eastarjet Adds New Okinawa Service to Seoul From Late October 2015   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
Korean low-cost carrier Eastarjet is planning to launch a new route to Japan, at the start of winter 2015/16 season. From the 29th of October 2015 the airline plans to operate Seoul Incheon – Okinawa route 5 times a week, making use of a Boeing 737-800 aircraft.
